			<h2><u>To Order</u></h2>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">You need to send a Bank Draft/Cheque of RM8,999 to our temporary office address below.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">Once our factory is ready for occupation, we will state our new address.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">You can apply for personal loan or micro credit, with any bank or cooperative in order to buy this canning set from us. However approval for this will be subject to normal approval process.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">Then you can pay on instalment basis to your bank or cooperative. This way you can buy this canning set from us as soon as possible. Once you got this loan from your bank or cooperative, then you can send us the cheque or bank draft to us as follows:</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">Please draw all Bank Draft under the name of “<strong><u>Eazy Canner Sdn Bhd</u></strong>”.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>Address is below.</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>Please send by post all Bank Draft to the address below:</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Eazy Canner Sdn Bhd</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>16 Lorong 5, Jalan Sentosa,</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Kampong Dato Onn</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>80350 Johor Bahru</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 20px;"><strong>Johor</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>Please kindly call Customer Service at 018-870 2422 (email : rahman@eazycanner.com.my ) for any enquiries before you make the order.</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>Kindly download and print the Purchase Order Form below:<br />
<a href="http://www.eazycanner.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/01-Purchase-Order-Form-Eazy-Canner-Sdn-Bhd.docx">Download<br />
</a></strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;"><strong>Please Submit it together with your cheque / bank draft to our address above.</strong></p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">Order delivery period : Please wait between 3-4 months from the date your Bank Draft cleared by the bank, for us to fulfil your order as we will only make an order from our overseas partner once a month at the 1<sup>st</sup> calendar date of each month after compiling all orders made prior to that date.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">Please expect some delay should there be sudden surge on order. We shall update you accordingly. Your patience and support is greatly appreciated.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">We hope to reduce this waiting period gradually.</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px;">We will launch our e-commerce platform in this website soon, so you can use PayPal, Credit and Debit Card later.</p>
<p> </p>

